¬–Z<?php exit; ?>a:6:{s:10:"last_error";s:0:"";s:10:"last_query";s:69:"SELECT wpw6_posts.* FROM wpw6_posts WHERE ID IN (1512,1500,1475,1393)";s:11:"last_result";a:4:{i:0;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:4:"1393";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2018-02-05 11:38:39";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2018-02-05 05:53:39";s:12:"post_content";s:8337:"<p style="text-align: justify;">In this ever-growing and competitive entertainment industry it is way too hard even for mature adult actors to get noticed but every once in a while, a child actor¬† with mark of truly something special comes along who is capable of presenting their potential in this industry -one of such child actors is <strong><em>Jacob Tremblay</em></strong>.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><em>Jacob Tremblay</em></strong> was born on October 5, 2006 in Vancouver, British Columbia. He is the second child of father Jason Tremblay who is a police detective and a stay-at-home mother Christina Tremblay. He has two sisters named Emma and Erica Tremblay who are also actors.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Career</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">This Canadian actor first stepped into the entertainment world via Television. In 2013, he appeared in an episode of the TV series <strong><em>Motive</em></strong> as Riley Stanwyck. In the following years, he acted in some episodes of TV series such as <strong><em>Mr. Young</em></strong> (2014), <strong><em>The Last Man on Earth</em></strong> (2016), <strong><em>Billy on the Street</em></strong> (2016), <strong><em>American Dad! </em></strong>(2016) and gave his voice to the animated adaptation of a children‚Äôs book series <strong><em>Pete the Cat</em></strong> (2017). Moreover, he acted in television short films- <strong><em>My mother‚Äôs Future Husband </em></strong>(2014) as Conner and <strong><em>Santa‚Äôs Little Ferrets</em></strong> (2014) as Ted Collins.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1396" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/jacob-tremblay-03-800-300x191.jpg" alt="" width="553" height="352" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">Jacob debuted in movies from a computer-animated comedy film <strong><em>Smurfs 2</em></strong> as Blue Winslow alongside Neil Patrick Harris. He also acted in short films such as <strong><em>The Magic Ferret</em></strong> (2013) and <strong><em>Gord‚Äôs Brother</em></strong> (2015) then he acted on an American science fiction horror movie <strong><em>Extraterrestrial </em></strong>in 2014.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">In 2015, he landed one of the major films of his career till date <strong><em>Room,</em></strong> adapted from the novel by Emma Donoghue, directed by Lenny Abrahamson where he played the character of Jack Newsome alongside <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/brie-larson-career-upcoming-projects-personal-life-achievements-networth/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Brie Larson</a>. He played the character of an innocent long-haired little boy who had been held captive with his mother since his birth. He beautifully portrays his experience to the outside world after he and his mother have escaped from the hostage situation. The movie was a success in the box office and the performance of Jacob was highly acclaimed globally.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1398" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/151258414-300x175.jpg" alt="" width="538" height="314" />

&nbsp;
<p style="text-align: justify;">After Room, Trembley got many movies offers and subsequently in the year 2016 he performed on films such as¬† a comedy movie <strong><em>Donald Trump‚Äôs The Art of the Deal: The Movie</em></strong>,¬† a dark fantasy horror movie <strong><em>Before I Wake</em></strong>, an adventure comedy-drama <strong><em>Burn Your Maps</em></strong> as well as a psychological thriller drama film <strong><em>Shut In</em></strong>. In all these movies, Tremblay performed extraordinarily and was critically praised.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1397" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Jacob-Tremblay-in-The-Book-Of-Henry-1200x520-300x199.jpg" alt="" width="545" height="362" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">Recently in 2017, he acted on <strong><em>The Book of Henry</em></strong> as Peter Carpenter alongside Naomi Watts and Maddie Ziegler and he also gave a soulful performance on an American drama film <strong><em>Wonder </em></strong>as August Pullman, based on a novel by R.J. Palacio of the same name.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>¬†</strong><strong>Upcoming Projects</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Jacob is an extremely proficient actor even at this age. He is to portray the role of Young Rupert Turner in the movie <strong><em>The Death and Life of John F. Donovan</em></strong>, directed by Xavier Dolan which also stars Kit Harrington and Natalie Portman among others that is to be released in 2018. He is also set to star in much anticipated American science-fiction horror movie <strong><em>The Predators</em></strong> which is a fourth installment of the Predator film series, directed by Shane Black and is announced to hit the cinemas on 3 August 2018.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1399" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/C5HugjjUEAAzWIn-300x153.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="273" />
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Personal Life</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Trembley lives in Langley City, Canada with his parents and sisters. He is a Lego enthusiast, enjoys hockey and traveling with his parents and friends.¬† He adores Marvel Superhero Ironman and is a huge fan of Oscar Issac as well as <strong><em>Star Wars</em></strong> movie series so much that he has named his dog as ‚ÄòRey‚Äô after the protagonist of the blockbuster movie. He is active on Instagram and Twitter with around 526k and 88.8k followers respectively. He also shares a good rapport with his co-stars like <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/brie-larson-career-upcoming-projects-personal-life-achievements-networth/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Brie Larson</a>.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1400" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/parents-300x256.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="371" />
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Achievements</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Undoubtedly Jacob has stolen many hearts with his performance mainly through his movie <strong><em>Room</em></strong> which consequently has led him to be nominated for many reputed awards shows and has even won some of those. Though he didn‚Äôt win it, he is the youngest actor to be nominated for <strong><em>Outstanding Performance by a Male Actor in a Supporting Role</em></strong> at the <strong><em>Screen Actors Guild</em></strong> <strong><em>Awards</em></strong> for <strong><em>Room</em></strong> in 2016 which is considered a milestone achievement for a child artist. Furthermore, he won <strong><em>Best Performance by an actor in a Leading Role</em></strong> by <strong><em>Academy of Canadian Cinema and Television, Most Promising Performer</em></strong> by <strong><em>Chicago Films Critics Association, Best Young performer</em></strong> by <strong><em>Critics‚Äô Choice Movie Award</em></strong> and <strong><em>Best Breakthrough Performance </em></strong>by <strong><em>National Board of Review</em></strong> and <strong><em>San Diego Film Critics Society</em></strong> for his movie <strong><em>Room </em></strong>in 2016. His role in <strong><em>Room</em></strong> also led him to win <strong><em>Best Actors Award</em></strong> from the <strong><em>Washington D.C Area Film Critic Association</em></strong>, <strong><em>Young Entertainers Awards</em></strong> along with <strong><em>Awards Circuit Community Award</em></strong>.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1401" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/rs_634x1024-160117181458-634.Jacob_Tremblay-jmd-011716-288x300.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="453" />
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Net Worth</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Trembley is a brilliant and witty performer. His net worth is reported to be $0.4 million.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">This eleven year old lad is an ingenious actor who always delivers splendid performance but still puts a humungous effort so as to improve his acting skills. As this young chap has a whole life ahead of him we truly hope that he continues to make us spellbound with his forthcoming projects.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="http://www.wikiceleb.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.wikiceleb.com</a></p>";s:10:"post_title";s:81:"Jacob Tremblay: Career, Upcoming Projects, Personal life, Achievements, Net Worth";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:76:"jacob-tremblay-career-upcoming-projects-personal-life-achievements-net-worth";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:95:"
http://wikiceleb.com/brie-larson-career-upcoming-projects-personal-life-achievements-networth/";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2018-02-24 12:06:22";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2018-02-24 06:21:22";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:28:"http://wikiceleb.com/?p=1393";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"post";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:1;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:4:"1475";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2018-02-25 23:55:43";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2018-02-25 18:10:43";s:12:"post_content";s:8203:"<p style="text-align: justify;">Growth, whether it is in terms of looks or in terms of acting skills, is what keeps you alive in the entertainment world and this Academy Award-nominated actor is always consistent in showing his growth in every project he delivers we are here talking about the British-Indian actor <strong><em>Dev Patel</em></strong>.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Born on¬†23 April¬†¬†1990 in Harrow, London; <strong><em>Dev Patel</em></strong> is the son of an IT consultant father Raj and a caregiver mother Anita Patel. At first, Patel attended Longfield Middle School and then completed his high school in 2007 from Whitmore High School by getting full marks from his General Certificate of Secondary Education (GCSE) performance.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Career</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Patel officially stepped into the entertainment industry from the E4 teen drama television series <strong><em>Skins</em></strong> in 2007 alongside <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/nicholas-hoult-career-upcoming-projects-personal-life-achievements-net-worth/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nicholas Hoult</a>. He portrayed the role of a British Pakistani Muslim teenager, Anwar Kharral for two seasons that was praised globally. Later, he appeared in an episode of <strong><em>Mister Eleven</em></strong> in 2009 and as Neal Sampat, one of the main and acclaimed casts of the TV series <strong><em>The NewsRoom</em></strong> form 2012 to 2014.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1477" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Dev-Patel-The-Newsroom-e1519580160131-300x178.jpg" alt="" width="533" height="316" />

&nbsp;
<p style="text-align: justify;">Dev‚Äôs popularity from Skins led him to land the breakthrough role of his career when Danny Boyle casted him in his movie <strong><em>Slumdog Millionaire</em></strong>. The movie was a huge success universally with a box office collection of more than $375 million. Patel depicted the character of Jamal Malik, a young Indian Muslim boy brought up in the slums of Mumbai. He played the role beautifully and gained immense fame worldwide after the release of the movie in 2008.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1478" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Slumdog-Millionaire-dev-patel-4152789-500-333-e1519580118858-300x197.jpg" alt="" width="534" height="351" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">After the success of Slumdog Millionaire, Patel was signed by many known directors. In 2010 he acted in an American action fantasy film <strong><em>The Last Airbender</em></strong>. Although the film didn‚Äôt do quite well, the role of Patel was well- received. In the following years, he featured in various films such as <strong><em>The Best Exotic Marigold Hotel</em></strong> (2011) which is a British comedy-drama film, a drama film <strong><em>About Cherry</em></strong> (2012) which premiered in 2012 Berlin International Film Festival, <strong><em>The Road Within</em></strong> (2014) along with a science fiction crime thriller <strong><em>Chappie</em></strong> (2015).</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1479" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/chappie.jpg.size-custom-crop.1086x0-e1519580309318-300x184.jpg" alt="" width="541" height="332" />

&nbsp;
<p style="text-align: justify;">Recently, Dev has delivered incredible performances in the movies <strong><em>The Man Who Knew Infinity</em></strong>, a 2016 British biographical drama film about an Indian mathematician Srinivasa Ramanujan along with another 2016 Australian biographical drama film <strong><em>Lion</em></strong> as Saroo Brierley alongside Nicole Kidman, based on a non-fiction novel ‚ÄúA Long Way Home‚Äù written by Brierley himself. He was highly acclaimed for his bristling and committed performance in these movies.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Moreover, he has also given voice in an English dubbed Japanese animated film <strong><em>Only Yesterday</em></strong> (2016) and a video game <strong><em>The Last Airbender</em></strong> in 2010.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Upcoming Projects</strong></p>
<img class="aligncenter  wp-image-1485" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/1178933288-e1519582553116-300x203.jpg" alt="" width="463" height="313" />

&nbsp;
<p style="text-align: justify;">Patel is a total delight to watch. He is set to play the role of Arjun in an American- Australian thriller movie <strong><em>Hotel Mumbai</em></strong> which will be released in 2018. He will also be seen in the movie <strong><em>The Wedding Guest</em></strong> which is to be released in 2019. It is reported that he will enact the role of David Copperfield in Film Nation‚Äôs new untitled retelling of Charles Dickens‚Äôs ‚ÄúThe Personal History of David Copperfield‚Äù which will be directed by Armando Lannucci.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Personal Life</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Dev resides in London, UK but owns property in Los Angeles, USA as well. He primarily follows Hindu religion. He also has a keen interest in Taekwondo and earned his first dan black belt in March 2006. In 2009 he began dating his Slumdog Millionaire co-star <strong><em>Frieda Pinto</em></strong>. Unfortunately, things didn‚Äôt work out between them and ended their six years long relationship in 2014. Lately, it has been confirmed that he is in a romantic relationship with <strong><em>Tilda Cobham- Hervey</em></strong> whom he met while filming for his upcoming movie <strong><em>Hotel Mumbai</em></strong>.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1481" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/PAY-PROD-EXC-Dev-Patel-and-girlfriend-Tilda-Cobham-Hervey-have-a-date-at-Echo-Park-Lake-e1519581176517-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="357" />

&nbsp;
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Achievements</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Being an overwhelming actor, Dev Patel has been nominated and honored with many reputed awards mainly for his work in movies like <strong><em>Slumdog Millionaire</em></strong> and <strong><em>Lion</em></strong>. He won <strong><em>Outstanding Performance by a Male actor in a Supporting Role</em></strong>, <strong><em>Best Actor</em></strong>, <strong><em>Best Breakthrough Performance</em></strong>, <strong><em>Most Promising Newcomer</em></strong> along with <strong><em>Best Young Performer</em></strong> from <strong><em>Screen Actors Guild Awards</em></strong>, <strong><em>Black Reel Awards</em></strong>, <strong><em>British Independent Film Awards</em></strong> and <strong><em>Critics‚Äô Choice Movie Awards</em></strong> respectively for his role in <strong><em>Slumdog Millionaire</em></strong> in 2008. Additionally, he was honored with <strong><em>Best Actor in Supporting Role</em></strong>, <strong><em>Best International Supporting Actor</em></strong> and <strong><em>Best Supporting Actor </em></strong>from<strong><em> British Academy Film Awards ( BAFTA)</em></strong>, <strong><em>Australian Academy of Cinema and Television Arts Awards (AACTA)</em></strong> along with <strong><em>Critics‚Äô Choice Movie Awards</em></strong> respectively for his movie <strong><em>Lion</em></strong> in 2016.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1482" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/dev-bafta-e1519581747100-300x191.jpg" alt="" width="537" height="342" />
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Net Worth</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Patel‚Äôs hype from the movie Slumdog Millionaire increased his net worth. ¬†The net worth of Dev Patel is believed to be $6 million.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Dev Patel is an extremely sincere and dedicated actor who can portray serious roles easily and with sheer supremacy which is the exact reason why his followers are increasing with every project he does. we hope that this driven actor will keep up his charisma and would soon be able to dominate the industry with his forthcoming projects.</p>
